  m_Name: QuestionChoice2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: "The Wolf offers a cluster of shimmering Stardust Flowers but pulls them
    back slightly. \"I have a special gift for you, but it\u2019s a secret just for
    us. Promise you won't tell the Starry Merchant or your Garden birds?\""
  option1: "I don\u2019t keep secrets from the people who help keep me safe. I\u2019ll
    tell them about your gift."
  option2: A secret gift? That sounds magical! I promise I won't tell anyone.
  option3: If the flowers are for the Eternal Garden, I should keep them hidden so
    they grow better.
